[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Top Hunter: Roddy & Cathy
	]em
	" is a side-scrolling beat 'em up that was developed by SNK for the arcades and was later ported to the Neo Geo CD and bundled in many SNK arcade compilations for more recent systems. It stands out from other similar beat 'em ups in that the player character primarily uses their own special weapons — extendable arms and yo-yos — to attack enemies instead of firearms, despite those same enemies often using firearms themselves. Those same firearms can still be collected from them, but only in limited quantities. It also has walking mechs that can be ridden for extra firepower, predating 
	[em 
		"Metal Slug
	]em
	" doing the same by two years. As for the story, it focuses on bounty hunters Roddy and Cathy as they hunt down the Klaptons, space pirates who just invaded the Earth and are now on an intergalactic run.
